{
  "stem": "2522.5",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "So in those days, Cooper Union graduate by the name of Rossi offered a scholarship for promising Cooper Union students to go to MIT Sloan School for a two year master's program.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "I applied for the scholarship.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "And before I handed my application, the admissions officer said, you got it.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "You don't have to apply.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "Because Rossi specially provided for-- for a scholarship for people of European background who are promising for America.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "And I said, well, that's fine, but Strassmanns don't take charity from anybody, and I will not accept your scholarship.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "So if Rossi wants to get me into Sloan School, I'll go and pay my own tuition.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "But I will not accept a-- a grant.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "This is part of the Strassmann heritage, you know.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 55,
      "text": "We never take anything from anybody.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 56,
      "text": "It's just a matter of principle.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 57,
      "text": "My wife has had-- really held this against me for the rest of her life.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 58,
      "text": "Everybody else considered that that was just totally outright stupid.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 59,
      "text": "The other thing, the reason why I left the Kubiceks, of course, is the Kubiceks were part of the refugee community, talking about refugee matters, talking Slovak.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 60,
      "text": "Really being alienated in the same way as the Borochov pyramid of my youth, told me these people were getting alienated.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 61,
      "text": "And I surely did not want that.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 62,
      "text": "By the way, in summer of 1949, after completing surveying camp, I went to Israel on behalf of the Jewish agency.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 63,
      "text": "Surveyed lands, Arab lands, near Latrun to divide it for-- for settlers.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 64,
      "text": "Got shot at, which was OK by me.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 65,
      "text": "They were very poor shots there, anyway.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 66,
      "text": "And so graduated from MIT.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 67,
      "text": "While at MIT, I told you I was working part time in civil engineering.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 68,
      "text": "And I was going to be a civil engineer.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
